[{"Code":"en","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix-introduction","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"27c5d58b-b114-49db-a8c6-a51661e47b2b\">Wix is a cloud-based web development platform that lets users create HTML5 websites and mobile sites using drag-and-drop tools. Its eCommerce system allows you to sell a wide range of products with easy setup.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">Payment Flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"30c84f3b-d8d1-4d91-8336-6ff63f4b7709\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(98).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(98).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\">Follow our <a href=\"/v1/docs/wix\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">installation guide</a> to start accepting payments with the Xendit on your Wix store.</p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix-introduction","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t0-5z4nx2-189\">Wix adalah platform pengembangan web berbasis cloud yang memungkinkan pengguna membuat situs web HTML5 dan situs seluler menggunakan alat seret dan lepas. Sistem eCommerce-nya memungkinkan Anda menjual berbagai macam produk dengan pengaturan yang mudah.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t0-yegote-190\">Alur Pembayaran</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t0-9axppi-191\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t0-zjbjod-192\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(98).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(98).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t1-bnd4dq-193\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs2s2t1-r4pbd0-194\">Ikuti <a href=\"/docs/id/wix\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">panduan instalasi</a> kami untuk mulai menerima pembayaran dengan Xendit di toko Wix Anda.</p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"27c5d58b-b114-49db-a8c6-a51661e47b2b\">Wix เป็นแพลตฟอร์มการพัฒนาเว็บแบบคลาวด์ที่ให้ผู้ใช้สร้างเว็บไซต์ HTML5 และเว็บไซต์มือถือโดยใช้เครื่องมือแบบลากและวาง (drag-and-drop tools) ระบบ eCommerce ของ Wix ช่วยให้คุณสามารถขายสินค้าได้หลากหลายประเภทด้วยการตั้งค่าที่ง่ายดาย</p><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน (Payment Flow)</h2><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"30c84f3b-d8d1-4d91-8336-6ff63f4b7709\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(98).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(98).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\">ทำตาม <a href=\"/v1/docs/wix\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">คู่มือการติดตั้ง</a> ของเราเพื่อเริ่มรับชำระเงินด้วย Xendit บนร้านค้า Wix ของคุณ</p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix-introduction","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"27c5d58b-b114-49db-a8c6-a51661e47b2b\">Wix es una plataforma de desarrollo web basada en la nube que permite a los usuarios crear sitios web HTML5 y sitios móviles utilizando herramientas de arrastrar y soltar. Su sistema de eCommerce le permite vender una amplia gama de productos con una configuración sencilla.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">Flujo de Pago</h2><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"30c84f3b-d8d1-4d91-8336-6ff63f4b7709\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(98).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(98).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\">Siga nuestra <a href=\"/v1/docs/wix\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">guía de instalación</a> para comenzar a aceptar pagos con Xendit en su tienda Wix.</p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null}]